Class SpiderResourceFound

java.lang.Object
org.zaproxy.zap.spider.parser.SpiderResourceFound
@Deprecated public class SpiderResourceFound extends Object
Deprecated.
(2.12.0) See the spider add-on in zap-extensions instead.
Class SpiderResourceFound is used to store information about found resources by spider parsers.
Since:
2.11.0
